label: SFX
description:
Berlin's Zoë Mc Pherson invites a diverse crew of producers to take a sledgehammer to their ace 'Pitch Blender' full-length. Featuring Jana Rush, Scratcha DVA, Gabber Modus Operandi's Kasimyn Gendang, Jessica Ekomane and MC Yallah.

Opening with a Scratcha DVA rework is certainly a way to grab our attention. The London legend offers a lush amapiano-inspired version of 'Lamella', slowing it down considerably to let the log drums ring out over Mc Pherson's sensual vocals. Without pause... more

label: Planet Mu Records Ltd.
description:
‘Flood City Trax’ is an exceptional debut LP of dare-to-differ footwork and warped post-Detroit styles by Nondi_, who hails from a small town in backwater Pennsylvania, and makes brilliant music defined by its detachment from IRL scenes - RIYL Jlin, Vladislav Delay, Helena Celle/Otherworld, Teresa Winter, Jamal Moss

So named for her hometown’s historic misfortune, ‘Flood City Trax’ is Nondi_’s first physical release under this moniker after years of digital editions under other aliases on her... more

label: EAUX
description:
Seth Horvitz's second Rrose album is a gloopy, sensual miracle, advancing the techniques they've been refining for over two decades and re-imagining minimal techno by harnessing the tactile gestures of deep listening music. Plenty of people have tried this, few have passed the muster: absolutely indispensable if yr interested in anything from Plastikman and Pan Sonic to James Tenney, Pauline Oliveros and Charlemagne Palestine.
